DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to explicitly annotate variable types in TypeScript using the colon syntax after variable names.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Everyday Types.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

