TITLE: Function Return Type Annotation in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to specify the return type of a function using type annotations after the parameter list.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Everyday Types.md#2025-04-20_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
function getFavoriteNumber(): number {
  return 26;
}
```

