TITLE: Correct Implementation with Type Guard
DESCRIPTION: Shows the correct implementation using typeof type guard to handle both number and string cases.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Narrowing.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
function padLeft(padding: number | string, input: string): string {
  if (typeof padding === "number") {
    return " ".repeat(padding) + input;
  }
  return padding + input;
}
```

