TITLE: Implementing a Generic Identity Function in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet introduces a generic identity function using a type variable T, preserving type information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v1/Generics.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

