TITLE: TypeScript Type Inference Example
DESCRIPTION: This example shows TypeScript's ability to infer types without explicit annotations. Here, TypeScript automatically infers that 'msg' is of type string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Basics.md#2025-04-20_snippet_18

