TITLE: Type Assertion in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use type assertion in TypeScript to specify a more specific type than what TypeScript infers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Everyday Types.md#2025-04-20_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const myCanvas = document.getElementById("main_canvas") as HTMLCanvasElement;
```

