TITLE: Exporting and Importing Types in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to export and import types using the same syntax as JavaScript values in TypeScript.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/handbook-v2/Modules.md#2025-04-20_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// @filename: animal.ts
export type Cat = { breed: string; yearOfBirth: number };

export interface Dog {
  breeds: string[];
  yearOfBirth: number;
}

// @filename: app.ts
import { Cat, Dog } from "./animal.js";
type Animals = Cat | Dog;
```

