TITLE: Control Flow Based Type Analysis in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how TypeScript 2.0 performs control flow-based type analysis for local variables and parameters. It shows type narrowing based on type guards and assignments.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/release-notes/TypeScript 2.0.md#2025-04-20_snippet_5

