TITLE: Defining User-Defined Type Guards with Type Predicates in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet introduces user-defined type guards using type predicates. It defines an 'isFish' function that acts as a type guard, allowing TypeScript to narrow the type within conditional blocks.
SOURCE: https://github.com/microsoft/typescript-website/blob/v2/packages/documentation/copy/en/reference/Advanced Types.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
